summary:
I am a passionate Student of Business internationally. I started and am accelerating my career in Business Development by studying an international business program at the Zuyd University of Applied Science.

I am genuinely interested in Business Development and Supply Chain Management. I have been working with all my heart to master all the business areas, enabling me to bring positive and innovative changes in the business world. 

Ultimately, my mission is to gain knowledge and skills about business in an advanced way so I can build my career, help companies grow their businesses, and achieve profit and revenue targets. 

Possess a total of three years of work experience as an assistant secretary and a Kitchen helper in Cameroon and the Netherlands: native English speaker and an elementary understanding of French.

My favourite hobbies are travelling, singing, listening to educative podcasts and learning about other cultures.

Please contact me here on LinkedIn if you'd like to stay in touch.
